## Part 4: Page Experience & Performance

### 4.1 Core Web Vitals Targets

| Metric | Target | Implementation |
|--------|--------|----------------|
| LCP (Largest Contentful Paint) | <2.5s | Preload hero image, optimize fonts, use Next.js Image |
| INP (Interaction to Next Paint) | <200ms | Minimize JS, defer non-critical scripts, optimize React hydration |
| CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift) | <0.1 | Reserve space for images/ads, avoid dynamic content injection |

**Performance optimizations:**
- Use Next.js App Router with server components
- Implement font-display: swap for Inter font
- Preload critical assets in `<head>`
- Code-split by route
- Use Vercel Edge for CDN delivery

